{"tid":2175660,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放不下 也忘不了","createTime":"2020-08-26T15:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T02:39:01.000Z","uid":112121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fdb952b8e7cdda2779cd1c29f9f06f0d018cf5","tid":2175660,"uid":112121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"我諗每一個人心裏面都有呢一個他/她，就算有再多既下一任，但曾經出現過係你生命既呢一個人，就一直存有一個特別位置係你心裏面。<br />\n<br />\n呢個人對你唔係特別好，外表亦唔係最出眾，但就係有一種感覺係難以取替。明知道無可能可以再愛呢個人，但就係放唔低。<br />\n<br />\n：分開無耐，你就同咗其他人一齊。我曾經諗過我可以祝福你，因為希望我俾唔到既幸福，人地可以俾到你。但原來見到你幸福然後身邊唔係自己之後，就明白點解呢個世界係無呢支歌仔唱。再睇翻以前既合照，發現自己同你一齊個陣既笑容早就已經無再出現過。<br />\n<br />\n如果有下次我會再愛一次 刻在我心底的名字 你藏在塵封的位置<br />\n 《刻在我心底的名字-盧廣仲》<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m78lJuzftcc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm78lJuzftcc&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=1ad4b276\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m78lJuzftcc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你生命裏面又有無一個忘記唔到既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0d62042e5bb0c817e4274f239f648a9c0ff60d","tid":2175660,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"算吧啦"},{"pid":"748e6fd45cf56bb8dfd2e3143f459c0e20c9a10d","tid":2175660,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"分左手咪好囉"},{"pid":"8bf2c45559c7e5533ca838b7f5b704676f3cf1d4","tid":2175660,"uid":244241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"刻骨銘心只有我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80596e67e95141195589b40876e1fae6e14101d","tid":2175660,"uid":371893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T23:32:54.000Z","msg":"有呀 但明知唔可能再一齊就真係放佢响心底就算"},{"pid":"fddc77aa74d248f9f75e0f207a139f1600de04f1","tid":2175660,"uid":112121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a80596e67e95141195589b40876e1fae6e14101d","tid":2175660,"uid":371893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T23:32:54.000Z","msg":"有呀 但明知唔可能再一齊就真係放佢响心底就算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T01:21:17.000Z","msg":"但有無覺得對現任唔住，好似唔應該開始下一段感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0f36b0f472ea40ee762d849730da418d7ccfdd","tid":2175660,"uid":371893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fddc77aa74d248f9f75e0f207a139f1600de04f1","tid":2175660,"uid":112121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a80596e67e95141195589b40876e1fae6e14101d","tid":2175660,"uid":371893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T23:32:54.000Z","msg":"有呀 但明知唔可能再一齊就真係放佢响心底就算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T01:21:17.000Z","msg":"但有無覺得對現任唔住，好似唔應該開始下一段感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"所以我到依家都仲單身緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我諗最鐘都會遇到一個更加愛嘅人 <br />\n如果沒嘅話,我就放佢响心但唔會再多諗<br />\n我覺得真係要準備好放底佢 先再出發去下一段感情<br />\n加油呀 我相信你最終會遇到一個更愛嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}